Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.30,0:22:39.05,Song,,0,0,0,,I'll never forget, looking up at the sky from this hilltop,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.05,0:22:47.52,Song,,0,0,0,,The morning sun so beautiful, on spring days, just us two.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.49,0:22:55.69,Song,,0,0,0,,All the hardships and the sorrows,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.66,0:23:03.87,Song,,0,0,0,,Carry them away gently from this hilltop,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.54,0:23:10.81,Song,,0,0,0,,together with the wind.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.81,0:23:21.22,Song,,0,0,0,,This vast, blue sky—may it never change,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.22,0:23:30.83,Song,,0,0,0,,And may my dearest friends stay just the way they are.
